@startuml
title CoWorker: Trend-triggered Daily Brief + Email Reply -> Draft Auto-Create

actor USER as "User"
participant SNIFF as "Sniffer (Shared)"
participant COW as "CoWorker"
database DB as "DB"
collections REDIS as "Redis (policy/idempotency)"
participant SYNC as "Synchro (similarity/ranking)"
participant INJ as "Injector (logic)"
participant GEN as "Generator (task)"
participant LLM as "LLMInterface (ainvoke)"
participant ADPT as "Adapter (constraints)"
participant ORCH as "Orchestrator (API)"

== Phase 1: Sniffer pulls trends; CoWorker watches & matches ==
SNIFF -> COW : (poll/push) trends[index_ref, items[]]

COW -> DB : getUserAccounts(user_id)
DB --> COW : accounts[]

loop for each account in accounts[]
  COW -> DB : getActiveCampaigns(account_id)
  DB --> COW : campaigns[topic, status=active]

  loop for each trend in items[]
    COW -> SYNC : similarity(trend.embedding, campaigns.topics)\n// 개인화된 임계치/리랭크
    SYNC --> COW : {best_match_topic, score}

    alt score >= threshold
      note right
        1일 1회 정책(계정/주제/날짜)\nUserPolicy로 다회 허용 가능
      end note
      COW -> REDIS : SETNX idem:daily_mail:{user_id}:{account_id}:{date}:{topic_cluster}
      alt already sent today
        REDIS --> COW : exists (skip)
      else first time today
        REDIS --> COW : ok(set)

        COW -> ADPT : constraints(account_id)
        ADPT --> COW : {max_len, hash_limit, schedule_support, ...}

        COW -> DB : getPersonaForAccount(account_id)
        DB --> COW : persona

        COW -> INJ : compose(persona, trend, /*no playbook*/, constraints)
        INJ --> COW : {brief, metadata, trade_offs}

        COW -> GEN : buildBriefTask.enqueue(brief, metadata)
        GEN -> LLM : ainvoke(brief → 지시사항 JSON)
        LLM --> GEN : 지시사항 JSON
        GEN --> COW : 지시사항 JSON

        COW --> USER : 이메일 발송(지시사항/가이드 첨부)
      end
    else below threshold
      COW -> COW : skip (no mail)
    end
  end
end

== Phase 2: User replies; CoWorker creates Draft ==
... (시간 경과 후) ...
USER -> COW : 이메일 회신(본문 텍스트)
COW -> COW : sanitize(body_text)

COW -> REDIS : SETNX idem:coworker:ingest:{thread_id}:{bucket}
alt duplicate reply window
  REDIS --> COW : exists
  COW --> ORCH : {status:"already_processed"}
else first reply in window
  REDIS --> COW : ok(set)

  COW -> ORCH : createDraft(account_id, subject, body_text, meta_from_email+trend)
  ORCH -> DB : insert Draft (state=draft, campaign_link?)
  ORCH -> SYNC : ingest(Draft) [async enqueue]
  SYNC --> ORCH : ack(queued)

  ORCH --> COW : {post_id, status:"draft_created"}
  COW --> USER : Draft 생성 알림(타임라인 링크)
end

== Optional: later by user ==
USER -> ORCH : (스케줄/발행/삭제 등 후속 조치)
@enduml
